vta.core

TensorLoad

Related Doc: package core

class TensorLoad extends Module

TensorLoad.

Load 1D and 2D tensors from main memory (DRAM) to input/weight scratchpads (SRAM). Also, there is support for zero padding, while doing the load. Zero-padding works on the y and x axis, and it is managed by TensorPadCtrl. The TensorDataCtrl is in charge of handling the way tensors are stored on the scratchpads.
